{"tid":1057663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(又改口風) 韓國瑜:沒說過會做滿市長任期","createTime":"2019-03-12T04:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T16:12:47.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"07ce1bb806967d27742ad93fd8dcc8456bfa6817","tid":1057663,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"等國民黨徵召佢選總統 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1552363695.A.12B.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1552363695.A.12B.html&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6PUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=4b444dcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1552363695.A.12B.html</a><br />\n<br />\n作者rathunter (老鼠殺手)<br />\n看板Gossiping<br />\n標題[新聞] 做滿4年&hellip;韓國瑜反問誰說的 <br />\n時間 Tue Mar 12 12:08:11 2019<br />\n<br />\nudn <br />\n做滿4年&hellip;韓國瑜反問誰說的 黃光芹發文還原現場解讀真相 <br />\n<br />\n被視為2020總統大選國民黨最強出戰人選的高雄市長韓國瑜，日前接受廣播節目專訪時，被問到4月是否領表登記參選？韓表示「不會的，會做滿4年任期」。11日節目播出後，再被問是否真的會做滿市長任期，韓卻反問「誰說的？」對此，主持人黃光芹在臉書發文表示要和韓市長「對一下」，甚至說韓市長「整個推翻也沒關係」。<br />\n<br />\n各家總統初選民調呼聲最高的高雄市長韓國瑜，在11日播出的廣播節目中，被主持人問到 對於2020基於正當性與否時是什麼看法，韓國瑜表示，「2020總統大選完全不在我的考量 之內」，重申「我現在最關鍵的事是要讓高雄市衝起來」，上任兩個多月來，感覺大部分高雄人過的越來越快樂。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://udn.com/news/story/12653/3691907?utm_source=udnnews&amp;utm_medium=fb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F12653%2F3691907%3Futm_source%3Dudnnews%26utm_medium%3Dfb&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6PUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=8af20a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://udn.com/news/story/12653/3691907?utm_source=udnnews&amp;utm_medium=fb</a>"},{"pid":"7a3ef711ad40999a350ea958fdd53bad68bf1c7d","tid":1057663,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:49:18.000Z","msg":"&rarr; q1qaz2: 想跑了 03/12 12:08<br />\n推 moonzone: 越想越不對勁 03/12 12:08<br />\n推 Athchen: 韓導 03/12 12:09<br />\n推 rick102233:  趕快選總統 兩岸統一就簡單了 03/12 12:09<br />\n&rarr; Benbenyale:  自己被冠上做好做滿都不知道? 03/12 12:09<br />\n&rarr; kawazakiz2: 現在歡樂，等弄巧成矬他真的上了就要哭了 03/12 12:09<br />\n&rarr; njnjy: 是擅長拍喜劇片的朋友呢 03/12 12:09<br />\n推 getwild: 高雄人過的越來越快樂..因為有很多笑話..尤其是觀傳局 03/12 12:09<br />\n&rarr; q1qaz2: 史上第一任就烙跑的市長要成真了嗎 03/12 12:09<br />\n推 artdeco1: 寒毒發威了 03/12 12:09<br />\n&rarr; excia: 越來越快樂是因為一直有笑話嗎 03/12 12:09<br />\n推 alinalovers: 沒關係啦，他這種施政態度保證撐不過下半年，再忍半 03/12 12:10<br />\n&rarr; alinalovers: 年就可以看人摔下神壇的好戲了 03/12 12:10<br />\n&rarr; <strong>njnjy: 史上最快宣布選總統的新科市長 </strong>03/12 12:10"},{"pid":"685c9a8b00bcfa1411c88d0e2694b359e587b0b5","tid":1057663,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"話唔定做咗一年就被人罷免"},{"pid":"7a997544c0ac7e312d37271ca205202c3ce36fa2","tid":1057663,"uid":191926,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"下屆常委<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n習近平<br />\n粟戰書<br />\n王滬寧<br />\n韓國瑜<br />\n梁振英<br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n崔世安"},{"pid":"fafb36ce5470b3fcafb9c01b2b7a6bcefb47f667","tid":1057663,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a997544c0ac7e312d37271ca205202c3ce36fa2","tid":1057663,"uid":191926,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"下屆常委<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n習近平<br />\n粟戰書<br />\n王滬寧<br />\n韓國瑜<br />\n梁振英<br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n崔世安"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜一統中國，取代習近平。"},{"pid":"be867d40d0091b1c381d1f62bff28aedd4590785","tid":1057663,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fafb36ce5470b3fcafb9c01b2b7a6bcefb47f667","tid":1057663,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a997544c0ac7e312d37271ca205202c3ce36fa2","tid":1057663,"uid":191926,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"下屆常委<img src=\"/assets/face